snippet: Officials took precautions in Afghanistan, and elsewhere, but rumored large-scale attacks did not come to pass.
abstract: Officials in Afghanistan, and elsewhere, take precautions over detailed threats of reprisals on anniversary of Sept 11, 2001, though rumored large-scale attacks do not come to pass.
lead_paragraph: Officials took precautions in Afghanistan, and elsewhere, but rumored large-scale attacks did not come to pass.

headline.main: Despite Threats, 9/11 Passes Quietly in Kabul
headline.print_headline: Despite Spate of Threats, Sept. 11 Passes Quietly in Kabul
